Package org.jboss.jbossts.star.annotation

Enum ParticipantStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ParticipantStatus>
      • org.jboss.jbossts.star.annotation.ParticipantStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ParticipantStatus>
    public enum ParticipantStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<ParticipantStatus>
    The status of a compensator. The status is only valid after the coordinator has told the compensator to complete or compensate. The name value of the enum should be returned by compensator methods marked with the Status annotation.
